room_title: Escape room "Blankface Operator" by Escape Room Delaware in Dover
room_description: You are a news reporter and you are trying to get your big break! A killer has been terrorizing the town of Escapeville. You have wandered into what you think is the Blankface Operator's lab. You need to find the murder weapons used, names of the victims that are missing, the real name of the actual Blankface Operator, and finally, find where the Blankface Operator is headed next.
